														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1244348">
									

<p>Sorry, but this doesn't really work for me. First off, that's an impossibly short formula for something with an effect like this. There's no way this stuff isn't naturally produced all the time. I'm also unsure why the Foundation is experimenting with this. The fact that it does more than kill you in a somewhat strange way is not exactly apparent, and I'm not sure the Foundation would pick up on that before they just file this away, never to see the light of day again.</p>

